N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 200.1 - Reproduction of New York State income tax forms

State Regulations

New York State income tax forms may be reproduced and
filed with the New York State Department of Taxation and Finance in lieu of the
official forms subject to the specifications and limitations set forth by the

New York State Department of Taxation and Finance. Notes

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
